### 私信模块接口测试

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token1 =
@token2 =
@userId1 = 1
@userId2 = 2

#####################
### 1. 发送私信测试
#####################

### 1.1 发送文本消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "你好,我想和你交流一下课程资料的事情",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 1.2 发送图片消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "msgType": 2
}

### 1.3 发送文件消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "https://example.com/document.pdf",
  "msgType": 3
}

### 1.4 用户2回复消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId1}},
  "content": "好的,我有一些学习资料可以分享给你",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 1.5 继续对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "太好了,非常感谢!",
  "msgType": 1
}

#####################
### 2. 获取聊天记录
#####################

### 2.1 获取与用户2的聊天记录(第1页)
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/chat/{{userId2}}?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 2.2 获取与用户2的聊天记录(第2页,测试分页)
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/chat/{{userId2}}?page=2&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 2.3 用户2获取与用户1的聊天记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/chat/{{userId1}}?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

#####################
### 3. 会话列表
#####################

### 3.1 获取用户1的会话列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 3.2 获取用户2的会话列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

#####################
### 4. 未读消息
#####################

### 4.1 获取用户1的未读消息总数
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 4.2 获取用户2的未读消息总数
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

#####################
### 5. 标记已读
#####################

### 5.1 用户1标记来自用户2的消息为已读
PUT {{baseUrl}}/message/read/{{userId2}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 5.2 用户2标记来自用户1的消息为已读
PUT {{baseUrl}}/message/read/{{userId1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 5.3 标记已读后再次查看未读数
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

#####################
### 6. 删除消息
#####################

### 6.1 删除指定消息(需要先从聊天记录中获取messageId)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/message/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

#####################
### 7. 异常情况测试
#####################

### 7.1 发送消息 - 接收者不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": 99999,
  "content": "测试消息",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 7.2 发送消息 - 给自己发消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId1}},
  "content": "给自己发消息",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 7.3 发送消息 - 内容为空
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 7.4 发送消息 - 消息类型无效
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "测试消息",
  "msgType": 5
}

### 7.5 删除消息 - 消息不存在
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/message/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 7.6 删除消息 - 无权限删除(删除别人的消息)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/message/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 7.7 未登录访问
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/conversations

#####################
### 8. 多用户对话场景
#####################

### 8.1 用户1给用户3发消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": 3,
  "content": "你好,用户3",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 8.2 用户1给用户4发消息
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": 4,
  "content": "你好,用户4",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 8.3 查看用户1的会话列表(应该有多个会话)
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

#####################
### 9. 分页测试
#####################

### 9.1 发送多条消息以测试分页
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "消息1",
  "msgType": 1
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "消息2",
  "msgType": 1
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "消息3",
  "msgType": 1
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "消息4",
  "msgType": 1
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

{
  "receiverId": {{userId2}},
  "content": "消息5",
  "msgType": 1
}

### 9.2 分页查询(pageSize=2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/chat/{{userId2}}?page=1&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/chat/{{userId2}}?page=2&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/message/chat/{{userId2}}?page=3&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

#####################
### 使用说明
#####################

# 1. 首先需要登录获取token,可以使用auth-test.http中的登录接口
# 2. 将获取的token填入上面的@token1和@token2变量中
# 3. 确保数据库中存在对应的用户ID(userId1, userId2等)
# 4. 按顺序执行测试用例,观察返回结果
# 5. 某些测试(如删除消息)需要先执行发送消息获取messageId
# 6. 会话列表会按最后消息时间倒序排列
# 7. 未读消息数会在标记已读后归零
